---
title: Crispy Mozzarella Chicken with Roasted Tomatoes and Potato Wedges
description: Think of this recipe as a new take on chicken Parmesan. Herbs, breadcrumbs, and mozzarella are heaped onto chicken to create a glorious crown of a crust. In place of marinara, roasted tomatoes add a sweet and tangy punch. On the side, you’ve also got some crispy potatoes because, hey, why not?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-mozzarella-chicken-8c82dbd7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crispy-mozzarella-chicken-aee9364d.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: North America
